reviews.review_text:
R & C Love the R & C, its nice to hear Vince not ragging to hard on it, he lets Jerry take the controls and that is great.

Lovelight is after GDTRFB but is not listed unless downloaded, the show is complete.

Nice recording, and if downloaded the songs are in order.
